 2009-02-11  Jason Merrill  <jason@redhat.com>
 
 	PR c++/39153

@@ -0,0 +1,22 @@
+! { dg-do compile }
+! { dg-options "-O2" }
+      SUBROUTINE CASHES(E,HESS,FC,FA,NORB,NPR)
+      IMPLICIT DOUBLE PRECISION (A-H,O-Z)
+      PARAMETER (MXAO=2047)
+      DIMENSION HESS(NPR),E(NORB,*),FC(*),FA(*)
+      COMMON /IJPAIR/ IA(MXAO)
+      COMMON /MCPAR / NFZC,NCORBS,NCI,NORBS,NORBX,NUM
+      K=0
+      DO 200 IU = 1,NORB - NCORBS
+         I = IU + NCORBS
+         II=IA(I)+I
+         DO 100 J = 1,NCORBS
+            IF (I.GT.NORBS) THEN
+               HESS(K)=FC(II) + FA(II) - E(J,J)
+            ELSE
+               HESS(K)=FA(II) - E(I,I) - E(J,J) + FC(JJ) + FA(JJ)
+            END IF
+  100    CONTINUE
+  200 CONTINUE
+      RETURN
+      END
